      <ul class="m-4 list-bracket md:space-y-2">
        <li>I&apos;M AN ENGINEER FOCUSED ON CRYPTO AND WEB3.</li>
        <li>BASED IN SAN FRANCISCO, CA.</li>
        <ul class="py-1.5 text-muted">
          <li><LastCheckin client:load /></li>
        </ul>
        <li>INTERESTED IN X, Y, AND Z.</li>
        <li>PREVIOUSLY WORKED AT:</li>
        <ul class="space-y-1">
          <li>üìä <a href="https://messari.io" target="_blank"><LinkButton client:load text="MESSARI"/></a> (<a class="font-code font-medium text-accent cursor-pointer hover:bg-accent/10 hover:ease-in duration-150" href="https://messari.io/protocol-explorer/all-protocols" target="_blank">ON-CHAIN DATA</a>), INDEXING BLOCKCHAIN DATA FOR VARIOUS PROTOCOLS VIA STANDARDIZED SUBGRAPHS</li>
          <li>üëÄ <a href="https://www.dapperlabs.com" target="_blank"><LinkButton client:load text="DAPPER LABS"/></a> (<a class="font-code font-medium text-accent cursor-pointer hover:bg-accent/10 hover:ease-in duration-150" href="https://flow.com" target="_blank">FLOW</a>), BUILDING DEVELOPER TOOLING FOR THE FLOW SDK</li>
          <li>üåÄ <a href="https://consensys.io" target="_blank"><LinkButton client:load text="CONSENSYS"/></a> (<a class="font-code font-medium text-accent cursor-pointer hover:bg-accent/10 hover:ease-in duration-150" href="https://bounties.network" target="_blank">BOUNTIES NETWORK</a>), DERIVING ANALYTICS FOR THE BOUNTIES EXPLORER</li>
        </ul>
        <li>STUDIED EECS + ECONOMICS AT <a href="https://www.berkeley.edu" target="_blank"><LinkButton client:load text="UC BERKELEY"/></a> AND WAS ACTIVELY INVOLVED WITH THESE STUDENT ORGS:</li>
        <ul class="space-y-1">
          <li>‚õìÔ∏è <a href="https://blockchain.berkeley.edu" target="_blank"><LinkButton client:load text="BLOCKCHAIN @ BERKELEY"/></a>, TAUGHT THE BLOCKCHAIN FUNDAMENTALS DECAL</li>
          <li>ü™Ñ <a href="https://www.innovativedesign.club" target="_blank"><LinkButton client:load text="INNOVATIVE DESIGN"/></a>, LED WEB VARIOUS DEVELOPMENT INITIATIVES (UI/UX + ANIMATIONS)</li>
        </ul>
        <li>SOME UNREFINED SIDE PROJECTS:</li>
        <ul class="space-y-1">
          <li>üçï <a href="https://sliver.today" target="_blank"><LinkButton client:load text="SLIVER.TODAY"/></a>, A DAILY PIZZA API FOR SLIVER PIZZERIA</li>
          <li>üîç <a href="https://nfty.fun" target="_blank"><LinkButton client:load text="NFTY.FUN"/></a>, A RETRO-THEMED NFT EXPLORER</li>
        </ul>
        <li><a href="https://twitter.com/mrbrianhobo" target="_blank"><LinkButton client:load text="@MRBRIANHOBO"/></a> OR <ClipboardButton client:load text="brian.ho@skiff.com"/></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
  <Toaster client:only="react" />
</Layout>
